hina-operations-2024-12-04/</link><description>通用汽车周三告诉股东，将对其在华合资企业记录两项总计超过 50 亿美元的非现金费用，一项与业务重组有关，另一项反映其价值下降。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 11:35:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/gm-take-more-than-5-billion-charges-china-operations-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>尼泊尔与中国签署“一带一路”协议，为项目进展铺平道路</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nepal-china-sign-deal-belt-road-plan-paving-way-progress-projects-2024-12-04/</link><description>尼泊尔外交部周三表示，七年前签署了初步协议，但此后没有取得任何进展，尼泊尔已与中国签署了“一带一路”框架协议，为项目合作铺平了道路。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 11:19:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nepal-china-sign-deal-belt-road-plan-paving-way-progress-projects-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞标：鲍威尔在韩国开球后开球，法国等待</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-12-04/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 11:08:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>拜登在安哥拉会见非洲领导人推进洛比托铁路项目</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-visits-angolan-port-city-lobito-tout-railway-plans-2024-12-04/</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登周三在安哥拉洛比托港会见非洲领导人，推进一项延长铁路的计划，该铁路可以通过洛比托将刚果和赞比亚的重要矿产输送到西方，并对抗中国在该地区的影响力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 10:20:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-visits-angolan-port-city-lobito-tout-railway-plans-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯财政部增加延期每日外汇购买</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/russian-finance-ministry-increase-deferred-daily-fx-purchases-2024-12-04/</link><description>俄罗斯财政部周三表示，将在未来六周内增加延期外币和黄金购买量。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 09:14:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/russian-finance-ministry-increase-deferred-daily-fx-purchases-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>调查显示德国企业对中国市场的信心跌至历史新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/german-firms-china-market-sentiment-falls-record-low-survey-shows-2024-12-04/</link><description>德国商业游说团体周三表示，在华德国企业的商业信心处于历史最低点，因为它们面临着中国日益激烈的竞争和经济放缓。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 09:05:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/german-firms-china-market-sentiment-falls-record-low-survey-shows-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>经合组织警告全球增长前景面临保护主义风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/oecd-warns-protectionism-risk-global-growth-outlook-2024-12-04/</link><description>经济合作与发展组织周三表示，如果保护主义死灰复燃不会破坏全球贸易复苏，世界经济将在未来两年实现稳定增长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 09:03:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/oecd-warns-protectionism-risk-global-growth-outlook-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>沃尔沃汽车报告 11 月份销量增长 5%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-november-sales-up-5-november-2024-12-04/</link><description>沃尔沃汽车周三表示，11 月份销量同比增长 5% 至 66,977 辆，其中欧洲和美国销量领先。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 08:11:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-november-sales-up-5-november-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>尽管美国实施新的出口限制，ASM International 仍重申前景</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asm-international-maintains-financial-target-despite-new-us-export-restriction-2024-12-04/</link><description>荷兰半导体设备制造商 ASM International 周三表示，根据其初步分析，美国新的出口管制措施与其早些时候的 2025 年前景基本一致。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 07:27:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asm-international-maintains-financial-target-despite-new-us-export-restriction-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>人民日报称中国可以接受GDP增速低于5%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-can-accept-gdp-growth-less-than-5-says-peoples-daily-2024-12-04/</link><description>官方报纸《人民日报》周三表示，中国并不执着于实现特定的GDP增长率，低于5%的经济增速是可以接受的，因为没有必要“崇拜速度”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 07:13:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-can-accept-gdp-growth-less-than-5-says-peoples-daily-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾和中国就新的南海对抗提出贸易指责</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippine-ships-entered-its-territorial-waters-around-disputed-shoal-2024-12-04/</link><description>周三，中国和菲律宾对围绕南海有争议浅滩发生的海上对抗给出了相互矛盾的说法，这是这两个邻国之间长期争端的最新争端。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 01:02:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippine-ships-entered-its-territorial-waters-around-disputed-shoal-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>打击中国电信入侵的美国官员敦促加强加密</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-official-fighting-chinese-telecom-intrusions-urges-more-encryption-2024-12-03/</link><description>一名致力于将涉嫌中国黑客逐出美国电信公司的美国高级官员向他的美国同胞提出了以下建议：</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 19:52:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-official-fighting-chinese-telecom-intrusions-urges-more-encryption-2024-12-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>